title: Think you're a Jedi genius or smart as a Sith? Take our Star Wars quiz and find out...
text: PUBLISHED: October 20, 2015 2:12 pm LAST UPDATED: October 20, 2015 2:33 pm Think you're a Jedi genius or smart as a Sith? Take our Star Wars quiz and find out... With the latest trailer for the sci-fi epic getting us excited to watch the latest instalment of the exploits of Han Solo and co, we decided to get together a quiz to separate the Masters from the Apprentices. Star Wars: The Force Awakens is the latest instalment in the sci-fi series
